<refsect1>
<title>Description</title>
<para>
The <link linkend="GtkMenuBar">GtkMenuBar</link> is a subclass of <link linkend="GtkMenuShell">GtkMenuShell</link> which contains one to many <link linkend="GtkMenuItem">GtkMenuItem</link>. The result is a standard menu bar which can hold many menu items. <link linkend="GtkMenuBar">GtkMenuBar</link> allows for a shadow type to be set for aesthetic purposes. The shadow types are defined in the <link linkend="gtk-menu-bar-set-shadow-type">gtk_menu_bar_set_shadow_type</link> function.
</para>
</refsect1>

